{"tid":393646,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣檢察官：「支那」不含貶意，屬中性用字","createTime":"2017-09-09T11:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T01:01:12.000Z","uid":35790,"like":107,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c432df272f0d95c57c1c1f23a294c52949af273","tid":393646,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:55:33.000Z","msg":"&lt;回帶&gt;<br />\n<img src=\"https://s24.postimg.org/ma90u8p2t/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs24.postimg.org%2Fma90u8p2t%2Fimage.jpg&h=5e8461e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">台灣檢察官：「支那」不含貶意，屬中性用字</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n台灣網民rial於昨日（十一日）在國立臺灣大學電子佈告欄系統PTT刊載一份「不起訴處分書」，這份由台北地方法院檢察署檢察官發出的處分書，明確寫明「支那未含有貶抑之負面評價之意」，並提出理據：一、「支那」在國語辭典記載中，是指中國、古印度對中國的稱呼；二、支那的發音與許多歐洲語言對China的發音近乎相同；三、我國（台灣）人民之主觀認知上，大多認為支那是China的中文譯音，不含貶意。<br />\n<br />\n網民rial稱，某甲在網上與一名支持中國的人士爭執，某甲查閱該人士的文章後，稱他為「支那五毛」，並在這名人士的文章留下「支那五毛」的字句，並與這名人士互寄私訊。這名人士認為被稱「支那五毛」乃是受辱，於是到台灣警察局提告，但台北地方法院檢察署以不起訴處分，亦即認為控告不能成立；檢察官認為，被告稱呼原告為「支那五毛」只是指原告是「中國的網路評論員」，而原告其他類似指控亦不成立。<br />\n<br />\n在不起訴處分書中，寫明：「然『支那』在教育部重編國語辭典修訂本記載係指『中國』，係古印度對中國的稱呼，且漢語中的『支那』和葡萄牙語、荷蘭語、德語、英語中的『China』以及法語中的『Chine』於口語發音上亦近乎相同，是『支那』一詞，於我國人民之主觀認知上，大多認為是『China』之中文譯音，而未含有貶抑之負面評價之意。」<br />\n<br />\n台灣網民rial上載的不起訴處分書：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/QbYhCOv-611x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FQbYhCOv-611x1024.jpg&h=01bee9d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/laHiNxO-618x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FlaHiNxO-618x1024.jpg&h=6baf37d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/6BBYugy-576x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F6BBYugy-576x1024.jpg&h=c2a1eb74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/PYVbXg1-621x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FPYVbXg1-621x1024.jpg&h=d289f5ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/06/china-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2017%2F06%2Fchina-china%2F&d=7vRNrQgXGmkLikA4BCDexU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=01893218\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/06/china-china/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/280155/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/280155/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"1992847c14a2a605015c01824ddafaf8017a85a9","tid":393646,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc626e82a7acee5682779bf2ab67adbf766f4dd","tid":393646,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:59:04.000Z","msg":"所以要搭賤畜兩字<br />\n咁先有貶意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2001b4cfecf7b6a885b771584325b5aff8b63d33","tid":393646,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"勁！咁都記得！"},{"pid":"2a849daa90020945b6bc93e6bcb792c11125ffa1","tid":393646,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:02:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以要搭賤畜兩字<br />\n咁先有貶意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n「支那狗」都唔算, 一定要有個「賤」字<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">愛港力掛「英國狗」Banner。    平機會：不能作出跟進</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metrohk.com.hk/index.php?cmd=detail&amp;id=207991 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrohk.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Fcmd%3Ddetail%26id%3D207991%20&d=7vRNrQgXGmkLikA4BCDexU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=c2486d83\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metrohk.com.hk/index.php?cmd=detail&amp;id=207991 </a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.inf.hk/media/2013/news/2013-03-26/20130326231559hkp81colbannerFILE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.inf.hk%2Fmedia%2F2013%2Fnews%2F2013-03-26%2F20130326231559hkp81colbannerFILE.jpg&h=3b2dd4df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「愛港力」上周到港台時展示一幅寫上「不要英國狗餘孽請早抖」的橫額，惹起多宗投訴，疑「英國狗」一詞涉觸犯《種族歧視條例》。 <br />\n<br />\n有網民昨公開平機會的回覆信件，平機會指研究是次事件的背景，橫額中的「英國狗」一詞，只意指與英國有政治聯繫的人士，並非針對英國民族，故認為不屬《種族歧視條例》下的種族中傷，不能就事件作出跟進。"},{"pid":"64076c1049f614b52e038aa59d7b5d2c745816a3","tid":393646,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:03:57.000Z","msg":"「中國」一詞先係含貶意<br />\n<br />\n「中國」= 「中心之國」, 即係指外國係次等"},{"pid":"7116af6439cbea9ba91b82dc1a9bee27efd2515e","tid":393646,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:05:07.000Z","msg":"改國號做 People's Republic of Zhongguo<br />\n<br />\n否則CHINA都係歧視"},{"pid":"6bd3f02357cb48b096cc0d32c2eaecb2458262c3","tid":393646,"uid":35790,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:06:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpfxRITL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpfxRITL.jpg&h=20b5f793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孫中山寫給日本首相大隈重信的信件中，以「支那」稱呼中國。（圖片擷取自網路）"},{"pid":"7b35fa7d5dfcfcc6c091bbdd5a9dc9965e722a23","tid":393646,"uid":46644,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:07:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"372ef1d750bf2c61ec63926c7079679449507338","tid":393646,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人都係支那人</blockquote><br />\n你就係支那人"},{"pid":"a2ab3ff82c61